1. *Osobno* se nadam da ću uspeti da ostvarim svoje ciljeve. (Personally, I hope to achieve my goals.)
2. Došla je *osobno* da me obavesti o tome. (She came personally to inform me about it.) 
3. On je propustio šansu da dokaže *osobno* svoje sposobnosti. (He missed the chance to prove his abilities personally.) 
4. On je *osobno* zaslužan za uspeh projekta. (He is personally responsible for the success of the project.)
5. *Osobno* me nije zanimalo da li je to istina ili ne. (Personally, I didn't care whether it was true or not.)